Description: Itera ASA is a Norway-based communication and technology company. The Company is a specialist in creating digital business, with communication, technology and innovation as the core competency tools. Itera delivers projects and services in cross-functional teams to Nordic organisations that see the instrumental contribution that innovation, efficient communication and smart utilization of technology can make to achieving their goals. The Company's core sectors are banking and insurance, public, healthcare, the service industry, energy and utility. Itera has operations in Norway, Sweden, Denmark, Iceland, Slovakia and Ukraine and delivers solutions and services to about 20 countries, including all Nordic countries.
